    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> 'Nduja</strong>, breaking it up with a wooden spoon, and cook for 6-8 min or until crisp and golden – this is your <strong>crispy 'Nduja</strong></p>",
