    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>fresh orecchiette</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>orecchiette</strong> for 4-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> orecchiette</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water </strong>(save the pot!)</p>",
