    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained orecchiette </strong>to the <strong>creamy tomato sauce </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
