      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> creamy tomato sauce with fresh orecchiette </strong>with the <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Top the orecchiette with the <strong>crispy 'Nduja </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>gremolata</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over the salad and serve with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong> on the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
